Edge To Edge We ve brought support for the new iPad aspect ratio In A Pinch Zoom in and zoom out with a pinch of your fingers.

Press on Now you can double tap to play or pause pan up or down to adjust the volume pan left or right to fast forward or rewind and pinch to zoom in and out. Get more control Based on feedback we ve increased the size of the playback controls Menu cleanup We ve adjusted a few things to make navigation easier: Watch is now My Vudu Under My Vudu you ll find Library all your titles Downloads and Offers Free Movies TV is shortened to Free and is now in the lower navigation

Navigate Faster Get to your movies and FREE movies faster thanks to our clean new look and navigation Downloads Are Up Rental downloads are back! Available on devices with iOS 12 or above Bug Blocker We ve fixed a bunch of bugs. And by fixed we mean exterminated.

NEW free VUDU account sign up You can now directly sign up for VUDU: watch select free episodes trailers for upcoming movies add movies to a Wishlist and much more! Bug fix: disappearing downloads As always please send the team feedback at iosfeedback vudu.com

NEW 3D Touch Picture in Picture Notification Settings 3D Touch: need to quickly access My VUDU Movies TV or your Last Watched Now do it directly from the VUDU app icon! Try it out on movie posters too! Picture in Picture for iPad: minimize the movie screen and do something else. Admit it we all like to multitask. Push Notification Settings: under My VUDU Settings Push Notifications select the offers and reminders that you d like to receive. Remember you must have notifications turned on to receive select offers. 3D Touch available on iPhone 6s Picture in Picture available on iPad Mini Air Pro updated to iOS 9 As always feel free to send the team feedback at iosfeedback vudu.com
BUG FIX: pre order activation not starting despite movie being ready to watch

BUG FIX: playback issue where an error popped up every 8 10 minutes. Thank you for your patience while we worked on solving it! The bug should be gone now please contact us if it hasn t. NEW: Do you want to Chromecast to a Vizio TV If yes check out this update! Issues or crashes Please drop us a note at iosfeedback vudu.com and include device model and iOS version. Thanks!

Check out the Only At Walmart link under My VUDU in the side menu to learn more FIXED No more video and audio playback bugs when switching between apps Cast trailers to Chromecast devices no account needed now NEW BUGS Copywriter on vacation which is why this section isn t as entertaining as usual. Sorry notsorry.

MAIN COURSE Introducing Spotlight: a purty new place to quickly find the best deals collections trailers free TV and more. We add new titles and deals just about every day so hooray for more reasons to look at your phone! SIDES The return and not a reboot of Search for My Movies My TV You can now watch trailers without signing in. Are you not entertained ! EXTRA GRAVY On the TV season episode grid we moved up the episode play button to align with the episode name. OCD much Some movies and TV shows dated got a little biz zay and suddenly we had bundles with both movies and TV shows together running around. Dealing with these multi format young uns wasn t easy. Do we put them in My Movies Or My TV A special section of their own The politically correct answer is now both. The playback bar now shows when casting with the iPad Mini. It previously only did on larger iPads but HR told us we couldn t discriminate against small devices. Sometimes play buttons would show up on TV series you didn t own. Gotcha! LOL. JK. Don t be silly. It was just a bug. If it really played you would have heard about it on Slickdeals. In some cases if you pressed play then quickly closed the player then repeatedly did that the audio would continue playing. You would not unlock a secret VUDU level or offer. This is not a Contra.
